column2: Now that the region of Patagonia and Araucania belongs to us, we should organise the area into a colonial government
Now that the region of Patagonia and Araucania belongs to us, we should organise the area into a colonial government
The Kingdom of Patagonia and Araucania

A lawyer by the name of Antoine de Tounens has ventured to the cold Araucaria filled lands of southern South America, known as Araucania, and has delcared himself King of Patagonia and Araucania, in an effort to stop occupation and colonisation of the region by the local powers.
The King of Patagonia and Araucania
Now that we've secured the lands of Patagonia it's time to free the Kingdom of Patagonia and Araucania with Orélie-Antoine I as its monarch and protector.
